=begin pod
=head2 add-section

Adds a section to the shortcuts window.

This is the programmatic equivalent to using L<Gnome::Gtk4::Builder|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/Builder> and a
`<child>` tag to add the child.

Using L<.set-child() in class Window|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/Window#set-child> is not appropriate as the shortcuts
window manages its children internally.

=begin code
method add-section ( N-Object() $section )
=end code

=item $section; the L<Gnome::Gtk4::ShortcutsSection|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/ShortcutsSection> to add.

